description.displayText: Nubia was a HUGE help for me with my toddler twins. She is so loving with children and comfortable multi tasking. I would highly recommend her!

description.displayText: Nubia worked for me about 10 years ago when my daughter was 18 months old and I had just had my son who was a newborn. She is amazing with babies and toddlers and showed love and caring to them every day. She helped with meals, laundry and light cleaning along with taking care of the kids.  Nubia would be great with any age child, I can assure you she is responsible and loving and we have remained in touch after all of these years because she became very close with our family.
